## 开发规范 (Development Standards)

### 代码组织 (Code Organization)

#### 目录结构 (Directory Structure)
```
/src
├── features/              # 按功能模块组织
│   ├── ocr/              # OCR识别模块
│   │   ├── components/   # UI组件
│   │   ├── services/     # 业务逻辑
│   │   └── utils/        # 工具函数
│   ├── calendar/         # 日历视图
│   ├── timesheet/        # 打卡记录
│   ├── salary/           # 工资计算
│   └── mc/               # MC追踪
├── shared/               # 共享资源
│   ├── components/       # 通用组件
│   ├── hooks/            # 自定义Hooks
│   ├── types/            # TypeScript类型
│   └── utils/            # 工具函数
└── lib/                  # 第三方集成
    ├── supabase.ts       # DB客户端
    ├── openai.ts         # GPT-4 Vision
    └── mom-rules.ts      # MOM法规引擎
```

#### 命名规范 (Naming Conventions)
- **组件**: PascalCase (e.g., `ScheduleRecognizer.tsx`)
- **函数**: camelCase (e.g., `recognizeSchedule()`)
- **常量**: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (e.g., `OVERTIME_MULTIPLIER`)
- **类型**: PascalCase + 类型后缀 (e.g., `ScheduleType`, `SalaryRecord`)

### TypeScript强制使用 (TypeScript Required)

#### 核心类型定义 (Core Type Definitions)
```typescript
// 必须严格遵守的类型
enum ScheduleType {
  WORK = "work",
  REST = "rest",
  OFF = "off",
  OVERTIME_ON_OFF_DAY = "overtime_on_off_day",
  LEAVE = "leave",
  PUBLIC_HOLIDAY = "public_holiday",
  TRAINING = "training",
  SUPPORT_INCOMING = "support_incoming",
  SUPPORT_OUTGOING = "support_outgoing",
  CO = "co",
  UNKNOWN = "unknown"
}

interface ScheduleRecord {
  type: ScheduleType;
  plannedStartTime: string | null;  // HH:MM格式
  plannedEndTime: string | null;
  notes: string;
  isConfirmed: boolean;
  targetOutlet?: string;            // 支援分店代码
}

interface TimeRecord {
  id: string;
  date: string;                     // YYYY-MM-DD格式
  scheduleType: ScheduleType;
  actualStartTime: string;
  actualEndTime: string;
  restHours: number;
  totalHours: number;
  normalHours: number;
  overtimeHours: number;
  overtimePay: number;
  notes: string;
}
```

### 工资计算规范 (Salary Calculation Standards)

#### MOM法规强制遵守 (MOM Compliance Required)
```typescript
// 不可修改的计算常量
const MOM_CONSTANTS = {
  HOURS_PER_MONTH: 190.67,          // MOM标准月工时
  OVERTIME_MULTIPLIER: 1.5,         // 工作日/休息日OT
  PUBLIC_HOLIDAY_MULTIPLIER: 2.0,   // 公共假期OT
  STANDARD_WORK_HOURS: 8,           // 标准工作日时长
  DEFAULT_REST_HOURS: 1              // 默认休息时长
};

// 勤工奖规则
function calculateAttendanceBonus(
  baseBonusAmount: number,
  mcDays: number
): number {
  if (mcDays <= 1) return baseBonusAmount;     // 全额
  if (mcDays <= 3) return baseBonusAmount / 2; // 减半
  return 0;                                     // 取消
}
```

#### 计算逻辑测试覆盖率 (Test Coverage)
- **必须100%覆盖**: `MOMCompliantSalaryCalculator`
- **测试用例要求**:
  ```typescript
  // 示例测试用例
  test("工作日OT计算", () => {
    const result = calculator.calculateDailyPay({
      type: "work",
      actualStartTime: "10:00",
      actualEndTime: "19:30",
      restHours: 1
    });
    expect(result.normalHours).toBe(8);
    expect(result.overtimeHours).toBe(0.5);
  });

  test("休息日加班整天OT", () => {
    const result = calculator.calculateDailyPay({
      type: "overtime_on_off_day",
      actualStartTime: "10:00",
      actualEndTime: "19:00",
      restHours: 1
    });
    expect(result.normalHours).toBe(0);
    expect(result.overtimeHours).toBe(8);
  });
  ```

