## 数据规范 (Data Standards)

### Supabase表结构 (Database Schema)

#### 表设计原则 (Table Design Principles)
- 使用UUID作主键
- 所有时间用ISO 8601格式
- 软删除(deleted_at字段)
- 必须RLS策略保护

#### 核心表定义 (Core Tables)
```sql
-- 用户配置表
CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users NOT NULL,
  employee_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  employee_id TEXT,
  position TEXT,
  base_salary DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  attendance_bonus DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  pay_day INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 7,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
);

-- 排班表
CREATE TABLE schedules (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users NOT NULL,
  month TEXT NOT NULL,              -- YYYY-MM格式
  date DATE NOT NULL,                -- YYYY-MM-DD格式
  type TEXT NOT NULL,                -- ScheduleType枚举值
  planned_start_time TIME,
  planned_end_time TIME,
  target_outlet TEXT,                -- 支援分店
  notes TEXT,
  is_confirmed BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
  original_image_url TEXT,           -- 排班表图片URL
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(user_id, date)
);

-- 打卡记录表
CREATE TABLE time_records (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users NOT NULL,
  date DATE NOT NULL,
  schedule_type TEXT NOT NULL,
  actual_start_time TIME NOT NULL,
  actual_end_time TIME NOT NULL,
  rest_hours DECIMAL(3,1) DEFAULT 1.0,
  total_hours DECIMAL(4,2),
  normal_hours DECIMAL(4,2),
  overtime_hours DECIMAL(4,2),
  overtime_pay DECIMAL(10,2),
  notes TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(user_id, date)
);

-- MC记录表
CREATE TABLE mc_records (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users NOT NULL,
  date DATE NOT NULL,
  duration INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  certificate_number TEXT,
  reason TEXT,
  is_paid BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
);

-- RLS策略 (必须启用)
ALTER TABLE schedules ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
CREATE POLICY "用户只能访问自己的数据" ON schedules
  FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);
```

### 数据验证规范 (Data Validation Standards)

#### 客户端验证 (Client-side Validation)
```typescript
// 必须验证的字段
const VALIDATION_RULES = {
  baseSalary: {
    min: 1400,  // 新加坡最低工资
    max: 10000,
    message: "基本工资必须在$1400-$10000之间"
  },
  attendanceBonus: {
    min: 0,
    max: 500,
    message: "勤工奖不能超过$500"
  },
