#### 技术指标 (Technical Metrics)
- **API错误率**: <1%
- **OCR超时率**: <5%
- **DB查询延迟**: P95 < 200ms
- **崩溃率**: <0.1%

### 错误追踪 (Error Tracking)
```typescript
// Sentry集成 (可选，预算允许时)
Sentry.init({
  dsn: process.env.SENTRY_DSN,
  environment: process.env.NODE_ENV,
  tracesSampleRate: 0.1,  // 10%请求追踪
  beforeSend(event) {
    // 移除敏感信息
    if (event.user) {
      delete event.user.email;
      delete event.user.ip_address;
    }
    return event;
  }
});
```

